HEADWORD: Epithesis
<hw>E*pith"e*sis</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., fr. Gr.
<?/ a putting on; <grk>'epi`</grk> upon + <?/ to place.]</ety> <def>The
addition of a letter at the end of a word, without changing its sense;
<as>as, <ex>numb</ex> for <ex>num</ex>, <ex>whilst</ex> for
<ex>whiles</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

